tafsir[52]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,"Allah no janntoo fii √ëalaande ummital ndee fow tawetee e mun."
  69,2,"Refti O mawniniri …óum ngal lamndal : ko hon…óum woni fii Darngal?"
  69,3,"E ko anndin maa ko woni fii ngal Darngal?"
  69,4,"Samuudu yim…ìe Saalihu …ìen, e Aadi en yim…ìe Huudu …ìen fennii Darngal du…ó…óay ngal yim…ìe hakkee kul huli maggal."
  69,5,"Samuuda en kan, Allah halkirno …ìe haacaango yottiingo satteende e kulaleeji."
  69,6,"Aadi en kan, Allah halkir …ìe henndu …ìuu…ìundu haa fe∆¥∆¥iti, tii…óundu e ma…ì…ìe."
  69,7,"Allah wurti henndu ndun e hoore ma…ì…ìe dumunna jemmaaji jee…ói…ói e √±alormaaje jeetati, ndu lanni fii ma…ì…ìe haa ka hatti. Yi'aa yim…ìe …ìen e ko…óooli mun hino halkaa e leydi, wa si tawii hara ko binndeeje tamaro yan…óe e leydi yoorundi."
  69,8,"Taw si a yi'anay …ìe fittaandu heddii ndu …ìaawo lette …óen yanude e ma…ì…ìe?"
  69,9,"Fir'awna e mofte adinoo…ìe mo …ìen, e ca'e lettiranoo…óe wayliteede …óen, woni yim…ìe Luutu …ìen, …ìe ardi e kuu…óe bon…óe immorde e sirku e geddi."
  69,10,"Kala ma…ì…ìe yeddi Nulaa…óo mun on, …ìe fenni mo; Allah nanngiri …ìe nanngal …ìeydiingal ko O timminta halkude …ìe."
  69,11,"Ko Menen woni, fewndo ndiyam …óam hummbunoo, ronndinoo …ìen wonunoo…ìe keeceele mon ka laana dogayka, ka Annabi Nuuhu lesunoo e yamiroore Amen, fii ko wa…ó…óo…óon e mun."
  69,12,"Men wa…óiri kan laana e fillayee makka on, waaju ko dallinoree e halkeede yeddu…ìe …ìen, da…ónda gom…óim…ìe …ìen, nowru nanayndu nana …óum."
  69,13,"Si Malaa'ikaajo halfinaa…óo wuttugol on ka allaandu wuttii wuttaande wootere, ko ndeen woni …ói…óa…ìiire nden."
  69,14,"Leydi ndin e pelle …óen …ìamtee, …óe mo …ì√±√±e mo …ì√±√±annde sattunde, pecce leydi ndi e pelle …óe sewi."
  69,15,"Nden …óum fow wa…óata, Darngal ngal daroo."
  69,16,"Kammu ngun seekora nden √±alnde, sabu jippagol Malaa'ika'en, hara hingu lo'i, …ìaawo ngu wonnde sattungu jogondirngu."
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en no wontiri ka seraaji maggu, njeetato e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìannitaa…ìe …ìen ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kin nden √±alnde."
  69,18,"Nden √±alnde, ko onon wee…ìitetee ka Allah, onon …ìee yim…ìe. Hay huunde e fii mon suu…óotaako Mo. Allah ko ∆¥ellitoto fii ma…ì…ìe on fow."
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaa…óo talkuru golle mun …óen ka √±aamo mun, on weltoroyay wi'ugol : Ja…ìee ! Janngon talkuru golle am …óen."
  69,20,"Min mi fellitu ka aduna, wonnde mi immmintinoyte, mi hawra e njo…ìdi am ndin."
  69,21,"Hara himo e nguurndam wel…óam, hakkee neema duumii…óo ko o yi'ata."
  69,22,"E nder Aljanna toowu…óo nokku e darja."
  69,23,"Aljanna mo te…ìateeriiji mun weli he…ìude."
  69,24,"∆Åe teddiniree wi'aneede : √±aamee yariron ko lorra woo alaa e mu'un, sabu ko ardinir…óon kon golle mo∆¥∆¥e e √±alaa…óe fe∆¥∆¥unoo…óe aduna."
  69,25,"Si tawii non ko jonnitiraa…óo talkuru golle mun …óen ka nano mun, on wi'oyay : Ee bone am! Haananiino lam hara mi joniitaaka talkuru golle am …óen, sabu kuu…óe bone ko woni e mayru kon, wa…óata haa mi lettee."
  69,26,"Hara mi anndaali hay huunde e ko wonata √±aawoore am."
  69,27,"Hara maayde am nden wonuno timmoode am nde imminti≈ãtaake e mun fes."
  69,28,"Jawdi am ndin nafiraali lam du√±angol lam lette Allah …óen."
  69,29,"Cemmbe e jaahu am ko mi wallitoraynoo fow bonntirii lam."
  69,30,"Malaa'ika'en wi'anee : nanngee mo, kombon mo haa e daande."
  69,31,"Refti naadon mo ka Yiite fii no o mee…óira nguleendi magge."
  69,32,"Refti naadon mo e nder jolokooje …óe junndi mun woni cappan…óe jee…ói…ói sogonal."
  69,33,"Tawde pellet, o gom…óinaano Allah Maw…óo On."
  69,34,"O reer…óintaano wo…ó…ìe goo e √±ammingol miskiino."
  69,35,"Gi…óo …ìadondiraa…óo alanaamo √ëalnde Darngal, ko du√±anamo lette …óen."
  69,36,"Wanaa √±aametee woodani mo, si wanaa ko sii…ìaa e …ìalli yim…ìe Yiite …ìen."
  69,37,"Hay gooto √±aametee ndin ∆¥i∆¥∆¥i∆¥iri, si wanaa yeddu…ìe e bakkondim…ìe …ìen."
  69,38,"Allah woondirii ko yi'oton kon."
  69,39,"O woondiri kadi ko on yi'ataa kon."
  69,40,"Pellet, Alqur'aana ko daalol Allah, ngol O Nulaa…óo Makko teddu…óo on janngata e dow mon."
  69,41,"Wanaa nde konngu…ói yimoowo; tawde nde yu…ì…ìiraaka wa gim…ói. Kono fan…óii ko gom…óinton."
  69,42,"Nde wanaa kadi nde konngu…ói mbileejo, tawde mbilewu hino seedi e Alqur'aana. Kono fan…óii ko waajitoto…óon."
  69,43,"Ko jippiniraande ka Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow."
  69,44,"Si tawno Muhammadu fefindino e Amen yoga e konngu…ói …ói iwraani e Amen."
  69,45,"Ko pellet, Men yo…ìtotono bmo, Men naangira mo doole e kattal."
  69,46,"Hooti Men ta∆¥ayno e makko …óa…óol yottiingol e …ìernde nden."
  69,47,"Alaa hay gooto e mo'on ha…óoowo e makko, himo da…óndii e fefindagol e Amen fii mon."
  69,48,"Pellet, Alqur'aana ko waaju huliroo…ìe Joomi mun …ìen …óoftagol yamiraa…ói Makko …óin, e wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  69,49,"Haray kadi, Me…óen anndi fennoo…ìe ndee Alqur'aanaare ina e mon."
  69,50,"Pellet non, fennugol Alqur'aana ngol, ko nimse maw…óe wonoyta √ëalnde Darngal."
  69,51,"Pellet kadi, Alqur'aana ko goonga yananaa…óo mo sikke alaa e mu'un, wonnde ko ka Allah nde iwri."
  69,52,"Haray an Nulaa…óo, subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, kala ko haandaani e Makko, janto…óaa innde Joomi maa Maw…óo On."
